OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start to the day with
OL,6,Frain and drizzle, heavy at times. Rain
OL,7,Feasing in the morning to leave the
OL,8,Frest of the day breezy and cloudy with
OL,9,Fjust the odd outbreak of light rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a mostly dry and
OL,12,Fbreezy evening with late sunny spells.
OL,13,FRemaining dry overnight with some
OL,14,Fclear intervals and the odd spot of
OL,15,Flight rain possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells. A largely dry
OL,19,Fday with just the odd light shower
OL,20,Fpossible. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
